injuries.longComment: A strained right hamstring has plagued Harris during training camp, but this is an encouraging sign. Head coach Doc Rivers believes Harris will play in Wednesday's regular-season opener against the Wizards, but the Bucks aren't ready to confirm that. The veteran swingman is set to serve as a depth piece in 2025-26.
injuries.shortComment: Harris (hamstring) participated in practice Monday, Eric Nehm of The Athletic reports.
